Redfish calls this the Manager ID.

"The static Redfish Manager ID representing the BMC instance. 
This option will appear in the Redfish tree at /redfish/v1/Managers/<redfish-manager-uri-name>.

Changed to your wording.
kick to next line?

The static Redfish System ID representing the host system instance
This option will appear in the Redfish tree at /redfish/v1/Systems/<redfish-system-uri-name>.
